{
  "abstract": "The Rockefeller Foundation has been associated\r\nwith ICRISAT since its genesis. Early consultations\r\nabout establishing a center such as ICRISAT were\r\nheld under the auspices of the Rockefeller\r\nFoundation, and ICRISAT’s first 8,961 accessions\r\nof crop germplasm in 1974 came from those\r\nassembled by the Rockefeller Foundation in\r\ncollaboration with the Indian Council of\r\nAgricultural Research, New Delhi.",
